DiagnosisDescription: Diabetes mellitus type II [non-insulin dependent type] [NIDDM type] [adult-onset type] or unspecified type not stated as uncontrolled with peripheral circulatory disorders
Hypertrophy (benign) of prostate without urinary obstruction and other lower urinary tract symptoms (LUTS)
Routine general medical examination at a health care facility
Acute suppurative otitis media without spontaneous rupture of ear drum
